{"tid":107954,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"咩係人生","createTime":"2017-02-04T20:00:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T20:22:54.000Z","uid":28644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"39053ec45fc900e3d026d60618f51fed4d0cc794","tid":107954,"uid":28644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T20:00:37.000Z","msg":"每條命都係一個機會<br />\n生命(life)係冇得改變<br />\n只有生命既情況(Life Situation)先可以改變<br />\n應該埋怨時亦多做事"},{"pid":"59771343cc5664b513d33ad9b3349b5bfd8472a5","tid":107954,"uid":28644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T20:02:32.000Z","msg":"壞事一定會發生喺每一個人身上<br />\n只視乎我地點面對同反應<br />\n<br />\nBad things happen to everyone<br />\nOnly difference is how do we confront"},{"pid":"770353c58287051e4a0a644f4715434c88e423ab","tid":107954,"uid":28644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T20:04:59.000Z","msg":"有時你可能會質疑自己<br />\n咁係正常<br />\n但一定要信念自己<br />\n<br />\nThere will be self-doubt once in a while<br />\nBut this is normal<br />\nYou must hold your beliefs"},{"pid":"dbffaef45d02ab978da067975302e82f5cfc8a40","tid":107954,"uid":80580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T20:11:05.000Z","msg":"總結係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77e3d914ccfc5257e31aef98fa8f667e0f93be3d","tid":107954,"uid":28644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T20:16:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>總結係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無需要理總結<br />\n你永遠擁有的只是現在<br />\n不要讓負面情緒控制你<br />\n你不是你的思想<br />\n<br />\nLife needs no conclusion<br />\nAll you will ever have is the present moment<br />\nDon't let your negative thoughts control you<br />\nYou are not your mind"},{"pid":"7760e3492a234253d6ab3ce4fd9d1e2ffdd8c4e2","tid":107954,"uid":74728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T20:22:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>總結係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無需要理總結<br />\n你永遠擁有的只是現在<br />\n不要讓負面情緒控制你<br />\n你不是你的思想<br />\n<br />\nLife needs no conclusion<br />\nAll you will ever have is the present moment<br />\nDon't let your negative thoughts control you<br />\nYou are not your mind</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁咩係思想"},{"pid":"f1ecd2304be6ff881c400197c193d9157276a14a","tid":107954,"uid":80580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T20:22:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>總結係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無需要理總結<br />\n你永遠擁有的只是現在<br />\n不要讓負面情緒控制你<br />\n你不是你的思想<br />\n<br />\nLife needs no conclusion<br />\nAll you will ever have is the present moment<br />\nDon't let your negative thoughts control you<br />\nYou are not your mind</blockquote><br />\n咁姐係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   其實我識睇中文"}]}